{"tid":760760,"cid":20,"subCid":0,"title":"究竟係benz定maybach","createTime":"2018-07-29T23:12:10.000Z","updateTime":"2018-11-14T01:48:28.000Z","uid":105782,"like":0,"dislike":5,"uniUserReply":9,"replies":[{"pid":"02b0cad2495f98956933f0f7aa38266d4cb80209","tid":760760,"uid":105782,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2018-07-29T23:12:10.000Z","msg":"抱歉冇圖<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <br />\n有隻車成個s class咁既款，車頭就有benz logo，但b柱位有maybach logo，車尾就有s500/s600同maybach字樣<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"1637cfd00196c2aa808fd8e7b4959167276d768e","tid":760760,"uid":156986,"like":1,"dislike":5,"score":-4,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-07-29T23:13:49.000Z","msg":"賓屎收購左佢做高配車"},{"pid":"2d523d08b52a430191f195af7022dad9bf8c137f","tid":760760,"uid":50595,"like":10,"dislike":2,"score":8,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-07-29T23:23:03.000Z","msg":"s600 maybach囉傻鳩"},{"pid":"f51121e5e37f9f924ac8c62a4500fa315d5f76a0","tid":760760,"uid":13558,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"quote":{"pid":"02b0cad2495f98956933f0f7aa38266d4cb80209","tid":760760,"uid":105782,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2018-07-29T23:12:10.000Z","msg":"抱歉冇圖<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <br />\n有隻車成個s class咁既款，車頭就有benz logo，但b柱位有maybach logo，車尾就有s500/s600同maybach字樣<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-07-30T14:11:24.000Z","msg":"爭咩呀，溝埋做......笨"},{"pid":"dde8c99a5b24b840d9c95ba1c862c1d9010693f9","tid":760760,"uid":3937,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-07-30T14:17:43.000Z","msg":"係Mercedes-Maybach"},{"pid":"edb5d47d46c434282928d01d07066009aea7b621","tid":760760,"uid":14073,"like":0,"dislike":1,"score":-1,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-07-30T14:37:07.000Z","msg":"Benz amg maybach係三間廠嚟"},{"pid":"310215b28516fcd0470f41fff045b8f0e27c9879","tid":760760,"uid":100760,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-07-30T15:56:03.000Z","msg":"crossover咗"},{"pid":"6600555c5302e611996748ba657f05c3e6cab244","tid":760760,"uid":73,"like":1,"dislike":0,"score":1,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-07-30T17:05:01.000Z","msg":"係Mercedes-Maybach S Class<br />\n<br />\n<br />\n千禧年初， BMW及 Volkswagen集團分別收購了 Rolls-Royce及 Bentley，此舉迫使當時的 DaimlerChrysler集團密謀對策，最終決定收購活躍於二十至五十年代的 Maybach，並於 2003年推出了以車長命名的 57（ 5.7米）及 62（ 6.2米）豪華車型。<br />\n可惜，兩款 Maybach除面世初期賣到車外，往後幾年銷售成績都未能達至廠方要求，最終車廠決定壯士斷臂， 2012年宣布停售 Maybach。歸咎「死因」， 08年金融海嘯當然是致命一擊，另一個原因是 57及 62源於當時的 W220 S-Class，到 05年 W221系新款推出後， 57及 62在科技上便顯得落伍，而且過大的車體，使用上確實會有不便。<br />\n2014年，平治將 Maybach重生，成為旗下子品牌 Mercedes-Maybach，首部「翻生作」 Mercedes-Maybach S-Class，便選擇於廣州及洛杉機車展中同步首展。"},{"pid":"e915d182aa023de6d53422f2552948f89c087a1d","tid":760760,"uid":213877,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-11-14T01:48:28.000Z","msg":"關你撚事咩屌你老母"}]}